# ImageAI — .raginclude for RAG knowledge base
# Generated: 2026-02-27
# Stack: Python desktop application (AI image/video generation)
#
# Glob patterns are resolved at index time.
# Include files that document how the app works for users.
# Exclude secrets, build artifacts, and proprietary implementation details.
#
# EXCLUDED (never index):
#   CLAUDE.md / GEMINI.md — may contain infrastructure details
#   Docs/LLM-Contracts.md — internal implementation pattern (trade secret)
#   Docs/Operation-Guard-System.md — internal concurrency mechanism
#   Docs/Claude Desktop Instructions.md — CLAUDE.md for Claude Desktop, not user docs
#   Docs/LLM-Logging-Full-Content.md — internal logging details
#   Docs/CodeMap.md / Docs/CodeMap_Generator.md — developer tools
#   Docs/CodeReview-*.md / Docs/GeminiCodeReview_*.md — internal code reviews
#   Docs/ProjectReview.md — internal review
#   Docs/Linux-VM-Setup.md — developer/ops setup
#   Docs/*Implementation*.md, Docs/*-Steps.md — implementation internals
#   Docs/UI-Improvements-TODO.md — internal todo
#   Docs/Video-Prompt-Lyrics-Context-Fix.md — internal bug fix notes
#   Docs/Veo3-Duration-Update-Summary.md — internal update notes
#   BUGFIX_*.md, LINUX_*FIX.md, REFACTORING_NOTES.md — internal dev notes
#   VIDEO_TAB_LOGGING.md — internal logging docs
#   _Research/** — internal research
#   Notes/**, Plans/** — internal
#   secure_keys.py — security management
#   *.log — log files

